      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, budget-friendly option for a buyer who doesn't mind a bit of character. The engine and transmission are fully functional, though you may notice some minor hesitations and typical wear consistent with its age. The exterior has several visible scratches and a few small dents, and the interior shows noticeable thinning of the upholstery. It is a dependable driver as-is, but it would benefit from some cosmetic TLC and a routine tune-up to keep it running smoothly in the long term.",
